  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The EndoCuff is novel flexible cuff that can be attached to the distal tip of the
      colonoscope and helps to flatten large mucosal folds during withdrawal.

      The study hypothesis is that the use of the Endocuff (EC) increases the polyp detection rate
      during colonoscopy.

      The study purpose is to compare EC-assisted colonoscopy with standard colonoscopy for polyp
      detection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
